  "title": "Small Business Planning in 3D:",
  "body": "<html><body><div id=\"block-ti-west-content\">\n<article>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--type--text--bleed paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><div class=\"hero__container hero__container--small hero__container--no-image\" data-hero-container=\"\"><div class=\"container container--max-width\"><div class=\"hero__text-container hero__text-container--center hero__text-container__small\"><h1 class=\"u-font-family-secondary hero__title\">Small Business Planning in 3D:<br/>Benefits, Protection &amp; Exit Strategies</h1></div></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><p>Examine how a simple 3D planning lens can transform small business conversations. This program connects three critical dimensions: stabilizing the workforce through core and voluntary benefits, protecting operations with business owned life insurance, and transferring ownership through funded exit strategies such as buy sell planning and disability buyout awareness. Clarify how these elements work together to reduce disruption, strengthen retention, and prepare for the unexpected. Walk away with practical language, positioning ideas, and a structured way to guide business owners toward smarter long-term decisions.</p><table style=\"font-size:inherit;margin:32px 0;width:100%;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding-right:40px;vertical-align:top;\"><strong>Pricing</strong><br/>$49.00*</td><td style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><strong>Webinar Duration</strong><br/>60 minutes</td><td style=\"vertical-align:top;\"><strong>CE Requirements</strong><br/><a href=\"https://web.theinstitutes.org/ceu/state-requirements\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Verify your state and license CE requirements</a></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--tex